{"tid":892614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裸女無遮點奔跑重慶鬧區　高喊「打倒共產黨」","createTime":"2018-11-07T04:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T05:28:54.000Z","uid":35468,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6bf5e3ee027fe6b4f49e209246c7d0178c6960","tid":892614,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:14:39.000Z","msg":"中國重慶的一處鬧區街頭，驚現一名裸女完全無所遮掩，直接高喊「打倒共產黨，還我公道」，驚呆現場不少民眾。"},{"pid":"e44fef5f8869971c9b986dadadec679b9419b2e6","tid":892614,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:15:08.000Z","msg":"流亡芬蘭的中國異議人士李方，近日在推特上分享這段影像，影片中看到一名女子全身赤裸，站在鬧廣場上行走，更一邊大喊「打倒共產黨，還我公道」。雖然現場可見有警察和保全已出面維持秩序，甚至拿外套給女子穿，但女子一律拒絕，更把保全或警方給的衣物直接甩在地上。畫面也可見，現場有不少民眾圍觀，也有不少人看傻眼。"},{"pid":"d975afc4b9513651630a36ca944b57ab15897e64","tid":892614,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"而網友也紛紛在李方的推特上留言：「真可憐要全身光溜溜！才能讓人看到妳的訴求。」、「所以才悲哀，非要用這樣來做抗爭。頂多被當做神經病。」、「會被中共『精神病』了！」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"865be4668e66c9f651b2d3718b24c24526340dda","tid":892614,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181106/1461244/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181106%2F1461244%2F&d=sm4UzQuaDl%2B6eTsmviJ43P755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d5be26d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181106%2F1461244%2F&h=7c3a1ac8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181106/1461244/</a><br />\n建立時間：2018/11/06 14:51"},{"pid":"0120e4070259bac8df173d8ce678b6aac554d386","tid":892614,"uid":39226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:16:14.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"379e286d5c804e402995e51546d93900a099b860","tid":892614,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"